text.tspan: Note: Red arrows show cycles (..) | Blue arrows show structure

div.p: Traditional paths like /home/user look like hierarchies, but the underlying inode graph is a Directed Cyclic Graph.

ol.li: Cycles: Created by .. entries pointing to parent inodes.
DAG Property: Filesystem without .. and hard links is a DAG.
Hard Links: Convergence of multiple edges (user/file.txt, tmp/backup.txt) on Inode 5.
